wiki.summary: There are officially three versions of this song to date. Two versions were released May 15th, 2017 on blonded RADIO, each with a different verse from Frank Ocean. This is the third version for the album, which includes both verses, extending the track past the run-times of the first two original versions. “RAF” (released as a single via streaming) “RAF (Version 2)” (never released with a CDQ) “RAF (Album Version)” (this version) This song was also featured in Madden NFL 18. Read more on Last.fm.
